{"tid":2109308,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"白宮今日發布簡報聲明","createTime":"2020-07-15T06:59:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T07:30:13.000Z","uid":238660,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"29d736a539236bfeff840be68917cde8505ffc27","tid":2109308,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T06:59:28.000Z","msg":"白宮今日發布簡報聲明，表示總統特朗普已簽署行政令，強調在港區國安法的強制施行下，決定全面取消香港特殊待遇，香港將與中國大陸同等對待。<br />\n<br />\n📍行政令內容主要包括：<br />\n<br />\n1. 取消對香港護照持有人的特殊待遇。<br />\n<br />\n2. 撤銷出口許可證豁免。<br />\n<br />\n3. 有意向暫停執行美港引渡條約和犯人轉移協定。<br />\n<br />\n4. 停止為香港警察或其他安全部門提供訓練。<br />\n<br />\n5. 暫停美國地質調查局與香港中文大學空間與地球信息科學研究所之間的合作。<br />\n<br />\n6. 結束與中國和香港之間的Fullbright學者交流計畫。<br />\n<br />\n7. 有意向終止美港之間的國際船舶稅收互惠協議。<br />\n<br />\n8. 基於人道主義考慮，重新分配給香港居民的難民名額。<br />\n<br />\n9. 對直接或間接在港施行國安法的人士，侵害香港民主、自治、和平的人士，限制香港言論自由及媒體自由的人士，進行制裁。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<a href=\"https://twitter.com/initiumnews/status/1283239159914610691?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Finitiumnews%2Fstatus%2F1283239159914610691%3Fs%3D21&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5Guw%2BoCD4UrwaevtQIqI6x5z0%3D&h=1851edfe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Finitiumnews%2Fstatus%2F1283239159914610691%3Fs%3D21&h=fb4eb3fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/initiumnews/status/1283239159914610691?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25970b8b6415044366da9afd057d078246cc58c2","tid":2109308,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T07:00:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2bc6289b15f98a05480a2cbb86ffa4850fee6431","tid":2109308,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T07:01:02.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">民</span></span>"},{"pid":"0a72cc972ed2cc97c8b2f85d6a85181242d60969","tid":2109308,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020